				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">OK, inflammatory title aside:
<br />

<br />
<a href="http://money.cnn.com/2004/12/01/news/fortune500/jesus_ad_ban/index.htm" target="_blank">http://money.cnn.com/2004/12/01/news/fortune500/jesus_ad_ban/index.htm</a>
<br />

<br />
CBS and NBC refuse to air an ad for the United Church of Christ why? Because the ad specifies they accept anyone regardless of sexual orientation.
<br />

<br />
The ad campaign itself is featured at <a href="http://www.stillspeaking.com/" target="_blank">http://www.stillspeaking.com/</a> but the site is getting pounded pretty hard.
<br />

<br />
Fuck CBS.
