<br />

<br />
I think the right has long had a persecution complex about the whores in the media being out to get them, and frankly, after years in power I'm getting tired of hearing it.  The whores in media may have favorite patrons, but they'll fuck anybody for money, unless they lose more money from somebody else, or somebody threatens to hit them.  And since most of the recent presidents have been republicans, clearly the media aren't all that.
<br />

<br />
